         CLIPS (6.30 3/17/15)
CLIPS> (deftemplate number
   (slot value))
CLIPS> (defrule even_number
   (number (value ?n&:(eq (mod ?n 2) 0)))
   =>
   (printout t "The number is even" crlf))
CLIPS> (run)
CLIPS> (reset)
CLIPS> (assert (number(15)))

[PRNTUTIL2] Syntax Error:  Check appropriate syntax for deftemplate pattern.
CLIPS> (assert (number(value 15)))
<Fact-1>
CLIPS> (assert (number(value 28)))
<Fact-2>
CLIPS> (run)
The number is even
